name: 05-Predictive Analysis and Insights
content:
Predictive Analysis and Insights

  • Best Match Tower Predictions: Suggests the most reliable fallback tower for each outage scenario.
  • City-Level Diversion Insights: Aggregates results to highlight geographic regions with weak redundancy.
  • High-Risk Towers: Identifies towers with insufficient neighbor support, guiding infrastructure investment.
  • Operational Dashboard:
  • Neighbor mappings.
  • Diversion success rates.
  • Real-time load balancing recommendations.
